{"tid":1442893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"堵路目的係咩？市民無人明呀！","createTime":"2019-08-11T05:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:28:32.000Z","uid":101393,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"291847d5b1b187381f9da96c81a25bf3b22b77f6","tid":1442893,"uid":101393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:36:15.000Z","msg":"同路人當然心知堵路原因<br />\n但上到電視，人地睇到係為堵而堵，搞亂香港，為撚狗，為消耗警力<br />\n但五大訴求就上唔到電視俾全港市民睇到我地堵路為乜！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">快閃，都要留下快閃目的同痕跡，唔係障礙物<br />\n快閃，應該要留低自己訴求同原因！2-3人不停係快閃現場附近貼警黑同五大訴求，噴住痴，盡痴，痴完走！再唔係就一塊大字報鋪係路，寫低警黑勾結，垃圾政權！五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n咁樣市民先睇到我地堵路嘅原因</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我明前線已經好多嘢做，呢啲嘢應該係和理非做！但佢地做嘅令好難帶到上電視俾人知，因為唔juicy，拎唔到注意！<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法可能好似好左膠，但暫時亦係一個方法令我地想要嘅嘢帶返上枱面！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊諗下！"},{"pid":"975ff3e9ec6823876847323230e72ccf50a3a069","tid":1442893,"uid":101393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:36:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e627922a61929c7ee3c1f987ec5445e448a771cf","tid":1442893,"uid":101393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be0999b00a1914e52b8075bc452c5d5269ceff21","tid":1442893,"uid":101393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:38:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9460aa145e4bb99e25ca33cc648bd6175e8342a2","tid":1442893,"uid":101393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:38:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3eddefe1241123deed27466bdb9c168a473fd52f","tid":1442893,"uid":262329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:39:22.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n我無嘢講"},{"pid":"0c0fced6d7cee6e01190dd2e95a9db0a0b698cb5","tid":1442893,"uid":53233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:39:44.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"907b78eb0686030e1c5b5ba8a27d18c69aba3ff8","tid":1442893,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy"